#### Request for OTP for login
POST {{host}}/api/otp/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "root@email.org"
}

#### Login using OTP
POST {{host}}/api/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "root@email.org",
  "otp": "392551"
}

